<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وملك <span class="c2">(ولده)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> بعده.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
